    <title>electrum钱包使用trezoe one保存私钥的方法</title>
    <link href="http://danteng.org/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/"/>
    <id>http://danteng.org/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/</id>
    <published>2021-07-05T17:14:18.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-07-07T17:41:49.350Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>electrum钱包支持使用硬件钱包保存私钥，可在保证操作方便的前提下最大限度保证安全。由于私钥离线只通过trezor进行签名，所以无法窃取私钥。</p><h2 id="前提"><a href="#前提" class="headerlink" title="前提"></a>前提</h2><p>需安装trezor bridge。</p><h2 id="创建过程"><a href="#创建过程" class="headerlink" title="创建过程"></a>创建过程</h2><p>1，运行electrum。<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre1.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre1.png"><br>2，钱包处输入钱包名称，点击下一步。需要保证钱包名称唯一。<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre2.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre2.png"><br>3，钱包类型选择标准钱包。<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre3.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre3.png"><br>4，选择使用硬件设备。<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre4.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre4.png"><br>5，选择要使用的硬件钱包。<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre5.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre5.png"><br>6，解锁。<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre6.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre6.png"><br>7，选择地质类型并设置路径，下列三个地址类型分别是</p><ul><li>标准地址</li><li>兼容隔离见证地址</li><li>原生隔离见证地址<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre7.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre7.png"><br>8，配置钱包加密参数。<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre8.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre8.png"><br>至此，创建完成，在地址标签中可看到当前路径下地址。<h2 id="收币"><a href="#收币" class="headerlink" title="收币"></a>收币</h2>收币有两种方式，分别在接收标签和地址标签中进行。<h3 id="接收标签"><a href="#接收标签" class="headerlink" title="接收标签"></a>接收标签</h3>在接收标签中填写说明和金额，点击新地址，产生与之匹配的二维码。<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre10.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre10.png"><h3 id="地址标签"><a href="#地址标签" class="headerlink" title="地址标签"></a>地址标签</h3>地址标签中随意选择一个地址，右键选择详细信息，获得二维码。<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre11.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre11.png"><h2 id="发币"><a href="#发币" class="headerlink" title="发币"></a>发币</h2>1，发币过程与收币类似，在发送标签中填写收币地址和金额，点击支付。<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre12.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre12.png"><br>2，设置手续费，点击发送。<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre13.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre13.png"><br>3，在trezor设备上确认，币发出。<br><img src="/2021/07/06/how-to-keep-private-keys-with-trezor-one-in-electrum/070521_1447_electrumtre14.png" alt="070521_1447_electrumtre14.png"></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;electrum钱包支持使用硬件钱包保存私钥，可在保证操作方便的前提下最大限度保证安全。由于私钥离线只通过trezor进行签名，所以无法窃取私钥。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;前提&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#前提&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;前提&quot;&gt;&lt;/a</summary>
      
    
    
    
